uint32_t CSL_a53v8GetCacheLevelInD ( )


CSL_a53v8GetCacheLevelInD

Description
Reads Cache Level and Cache Type (D8.2.20 ARM Beta)

Arguments
None

Return Value
LevelInD - concationation of {Level,InD} [3:1,0]

Pre Condition
None Post Condition </n>
None

Reads
None

Example 

*
* uint32_t        Level;
* uint32_t        InD
* uint32_t        LevelInD;
*
*
* CacheLevelID = CSL_a53v8GetCacheLevelInD();
*
* Level = (LevelInD & 0x0000000EU) >> 1;
* InD = LevelInD & 0x00000001U;
*
*

uint32_t CSL_a53v8GetCurrentCacheSize ( )


CSL_a53v8GetCurrentCacheSize

Description
Reads the Current Cache Size (NumSets,Associativity,LineSize)

Arguments
None

Return Value
CurrCachSz - concationation of {WT,WB,RA,WA,NumSets,Associtivit,LineSize}
31,30,29,28, 27:13 , 12:3 , 2:0

Pre Condition
None Post Condition </n>
None

Reads
None

Example 

*
* uint8_t         Modes
* uint16_t        NumSets
* uint16_t        Assoc
* uint8_t         LineSize
* uint32_t        CurrCachSz
*
*
* CurrCachSz = CSL_a53v8GetCurrentCacheSize();
*
* Modes = (CurrCachSz & 0xF0000000U) >> 28;
* NumSets = (CurrCachSz & 0x0FFFE000U) >> 13;
* Assoc = (CurrCachSz & 0x00001FF8U) >> 3;
* LineSize = (CurrCachSz & 0x00000007U);
*
*

uint32_t CSL_a53v8InvalidateCacheLevelType ( uint8_t  level,
uint8_t  type 
)


CSL_a53v8InvalidateCacheLevelType

Description
Invalidates cache based upon type and level for all set/way values

Arguments
level - Cache level from 1 to 7
type - Cache type 0 = none, 001 i only, 010 d only 011 separate i and d 100 unified

Return Value
success - 1 if cache exists, 0 if it does not exist

Pre Condition
None Post Condition </n>
None

Reads
None

Example 

*
* uint8_t         level
* uint8_t         type
* uint8_t         success
*
*
* success = CSL_a53v8InvalidateCacheLevelType(level,type);
*
*
*
